'''Bhagivont Gerard Majella''' zaun aslo ek Redemptorist brother. To [[Katolik firgoz|Katolik forgojecho]] ek sant zaun asa. Bhurgeank, gorban aslolea bhurgeank, avoiank ani avoiponache besar aslelea ostoreank khatir tache magnneacho adar magtat.<ref name=cssr>{{cite web|url=http://www.cssr.org.au/about_us/default.cfm?loadref=65|title=St Gerard Majella|work=cssr.org.au}}</ref>

==Jivit==
Gerard Majella [[Italy|Italiant]] Muro Lucano, Basilicata, hanga zolmololo 6 Abril 1726. Tennem khupxeo milagri kelleo:<ref name=liguori>{{cite web|url=http://mission.liguori.org/redemptorists/saints/majella/bio.htm |title=Liguori Publications:Saint Gerard Majella |work=liguori.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117053729/http://mission.liguori.org:80/redemptorists/saints/majella/bio.htm |archivedate=2013-01-17 |df= }}</ref>

* Ek bhurgo dongrarsavn podon melolo, teka portun jivo kelo
* Ek gorib kutumbachea gonvacher axirvad ghatlea uprant, tem gonv fudlea vorsa pasun tankam pavlem
* Khup pavti goribank vant'talo te unde unne asounui tennem soglleank pavoxem kelem
* Ekda tennem utkacher cholon nustemkarank vadollantlean doriache ximer pavoilo

Sant Gerard Majella 16 Otubr 1755, Italiant melo.<ref name=Baltimore>{{cite web|url=http://redemptorists.net/saints-gerard.cfm |title=St. Gerard Majella, Redemptorist Saints |website=redemptorists.net |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808214147/http://redemptorists.net/saints-gerard.cfm |archivedate=2014-08-08 |df= }}</ref> Taka 29 Janer, 1893 vorsant Roma xarant Pap saib Leo XIII an bhoktivontacho mann favo kelo ani Dezembrache 11er, 1904, Pap saib sant Pius X an taka santacho mann favo kelo.<ref name="cathency">J. Magnier, 'St. Gerard Majella', Catholic Encyclopedia</ref> Saint Gerard Majellacho fest Otubrachea 16er zaun asa.

