Ekdam Sant Gerardan Pirofalo familik bhett dilo ani thoisor tacho rumal soklla podlo. Tea familichea eke cheddvan jednam taka portun dilem, Sant Gerardan taka mhonllem "Tujem kodem dovor. Ek dis tuka hachi goroz podot".

Khup vorsanim, Gerard Majella somplea uprant, tea ostoreche bhurgem zolmotana moronk paulelem. Teka brother Gerardachim utancho ugdas ailo ani tennem to rumal apleaxim haddunk lailo. Teach vellar, tacho dukh somplo, ani tenem borea bolaikechea bhurgeak zolm dilo. Hea ghodnnek lagon Sant Gerardak ''"il santo dei felice parti"'', mhonnge "borea zolmacho sant", mhonnon pachartat.<ref name=Tobin>{{cite web|url=http://cssr.com/english/saintsblessed/stmajella.shtml|title=Redemptorist|work=cssr.com}}</ref>

